FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Got questions about our food app? We've got answers!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does the food app work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app allows you to browse restaurants, view menus, place orders, and track deliveries all in one place. Simply download, create an account, and start exploring delicious options near you!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Is there a minimum order amount?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Minimum order amounts may vary depending on the restaurant. You can easily see any minimum order requirements on each restaurant's page within the app.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How do I track my order?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Once your order is confirmed, you can track its status in real-time through the app. You'll receive updates on when your food is being prepared, picked up, and out for delivery.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Absolutely! Many restaurants offer customization options for their dishes. Look for the 'Customize' button when selecting menu items to add or remove ingredients according to your preferences.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: We accept a variety of payment methods including credit/debit cards, digital wallets, and in some areas, cash on delivery. You can manage your payment options in the app settings.
PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Food App
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the food ordering process work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app makes ordering food simple. Browse restaurants, select your dishes, customize as needed, and checkout. You can track your order in real-time and receive notifications about its status.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Delivery fees vary depending on the restaurant and your location. The exact fee will be displayed before you complete your order. We also offer a subscription service for free delivery on eligible orders.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Can I schedule orders in advance?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Yes! Our app allows you to schedule orders up to a week in advance. Simply select your desired delivery date and time during checkout.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: How can I provide feedback on my order?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: After each order, you'll have the opportunity to rate both the restaurant and the delivery service. You can also leave detailed feedback or contact our customer support team directly through the app.
